data.description: You will not want to miss this amazing ranch in northwest Portsmouth! Completely renovated in 2020, this home sits on nearly a half acre corner lot, leading into a small cul-de-sac. This serene location boasts updated cabinets and countertops, flooring, paints, fixtures, and more! Easy access to bases and interstates, this home will not last! Conveniently located, yet far enough away for peace and quiet.
